org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.HRM.HwLogical.HwCommunication

Interface HwMedia

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CommunicationMedia, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HwCommunicationResource, HwResource, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ProcessingResource, Resource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    HwBridge, HwBus
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HwBridgeImpl, HwBusImpl, HwMediaImpl

    public interface HwMedia
extends CommunicationMedia, HwCommunicationResource
    A representation of the model object 'Hw Media'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Band Width
    • Arbiters
    See Also:
    HwCommunicationPackage.getHwMedia()
